title: Good Morning, Mr. President! - Novel Updates
genre: Comedy   Josei   Romance   Slice of Life
tags: Beautiful Female Lead   Childcare   Family Conflict   Female Protagonist   Handsome Male Lead   Misunderstandings   Modern Day   Politics   Pregnancy   R*pe   Wealthy Characters
author: Nan YinYin   南音音
description:
Accidentally, she got pregnant.

She went to the hospital to abort the baby, the whole country’s hospitals did not dare to operate on her.

Five years later, a nobleman broke into her world and suddenly took her child away.

What? He’s the child’s father?

Not only that, but he’s also one of the top country’s President?

So… … Am I not just dreaming?>
